MST_UNIT_EXPLAIN_AFFINITY_100002104^For a long time, now, have I joined your battles.<br>I thought you would lord it over me, but...it would seem I misjudged you.^與你並肩戰鬥了這麼久，<br>我雖然想認定你為君主……<br>不過看起來你並不適合。^그대와 함께 싸운 지도 오랜 시간이 흘렀군.<br>내 주군으로 모시고 싶을 정도지만……<br>그대는 굳이 원치 않겠지.^Nous avons combattu pendant des années. Je croyais que tu rechercherais mon admiration, mais... tu n'es pas de ce genre-là.^Anfangs dachte ich, du wolltest mir nur imponieren.<br>Aber heute weiß ich, dass ich dich unterschätzt hatte.^Nuestra contienda en conjunto ha sido larga.<br>Esperaba que reclamases mi admiración, pero... parece que te he subestimado. 
